Structure. Body 1.4 times as long as wide. Antenna 9-segmented, 1.8 times as long as forewing pad. Marginal setae on forewing pad weakly capitate, long and medium long setae, the longer ones often longer than distance between bases of adjacent setae; setae on dorsum of wing pads pointed. Circumanal ring medium large, weakly indented anteriorly (
Fig. 174
).

Measurements (in mm) and ratios (
1 immature
). Body length 2.06, antenna length 1.20.
